tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE influencer_campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(50),
    influencer_name VARCHAR(50),
    conversion_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
    roi DECIMAL(8,2)
)

CREATE TABLE BrandConversionRates (
    brand_id INT NOT NULL,
    influencer_id INT NOT NULL,
    conversion_rate DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    campaign_date DATE NOT NULL,
    ROI DECIMAL NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE InfluencerCampaignStats (
    influencer_id INT NOT NULL,
    campaign_id INT NOT NULL,
    impressions INT NOT NULL,
    clicks INT NOT NULL,
    engagement_rate DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    revenue DECIMAL NOT NULL
);
CREATE TABLE Influencers (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR, followers INT, engagement_rate FLOAT)
CREATE TABLE Campaigns (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR, start_date DATE, end_date DATE, budget DECIMAL(10,2))
CREATE TABLE ConversionRates (id INT PRIMARY KEY, campaign_id INT, influencer_id INT, conversion_rate FLOAT, roi DECIMAL(10,2))

CREATE TABLE Conversion (
	conversion_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	campaign_id INT,
	influencer_id INT,
	conversion_date DATE,
	conversion_rate DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_id INT NOT NULL,
    influencer_id INT NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(10, 2)
);
